data.description: Welcome home to 209 Lando Dr, a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem located in the coveted Lakeview Estates of Spotsylvania. Situated in a tranquil neighborhood, this residence exudes warmth and comfort while situated in the perfect location.   Upon entering, you are greeted with an airy, open-concept floor plan. The heart of the home—the kitchen—is designed for both functionality and gatherings, seamlessly flowing into the expansive living area.  Outside,  the back yard with trees setting a perfect backdrop for weekend BBQs, gardening, or just soaking up the sun.  Plenty of space for fun activites!  Convenience is paramount here. Enjoy quick drives to the local school, ensuring mornings are a breeze for families. Nearby parks promise weekends filled with nature and play, while the Spotsylvania Courthouse and other essential amenities are just around the corner.  Don't miss the opportunity to call 209 Lando Dr your home. In a location like this, paired comfort of Lakeview Estates, this property is bound to be snatched up quickly. Book your private tour today!  FRESHLY PAINTED  ROOF - 5 YEARS YOUNG HVAC - 3 YEARS YOUNG ALL PLUMBING PEX
